\n### Build\n\n```bash\n$ yarn build\n# MacOS\n$ yarn pack:osx\n# Windows\n$ yarn pack:win\n```\n\n## Copyright\n\n- **Author:** [canisminor1990](https://github.com/canisminor1990)\n- **QQ:** 4007338\n- **Email:** <i@canisminor.cc>\n- **License:** [MIT](https://tldrlegal.com/license/mit-license)\n","title":"Bilibili Clinet"}